thread.title: This Instagram famous puppy is so trendy in all the ways
thread.title_full: This Instagram famous puppy is so trendy in all the ways

author: Rachel Charlene Lewis
title: This Instagram famous puppy is so trendy in all the ways
text:
This Instagram famous puppy is so trendy in all the ways On the list of things we want in life, a precious puppy of our very own pretty much tops the list. As a result, we spend way too much time scrolling through totally adorable animal Instagrams . So when we came across @ps.ny, the home of both amazing vegan food adventures AND a gorgeous Instagram famous puppy, we knew we’d found an account we could spend way, way too much scrolling through.
Nothing is cuter than a trendy puppy , and this one is such a beauty! We heart this teensy creature, and we think you’re gonna love him, too.
Meet Cookie, the most ADORABLE Instagram famous puppy we’ve ever come across. A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 29, 2016 at 12:53pm PST 
Seriously, talk about puppy goals. Our hearts are bursting! A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Jan 4, 2017 at 7:02am PST 
Cookie is always on trend, whether we’re talking food or fashion. Just look at that little face! A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Jan 5, 2017 at 5:22am PST 
This precious pooch knows how to pose just right for every single shot. A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 31, 2016 at 10:19am PST 
Even when he naps, he naps in style. We dig it. A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 28, 2016 at 6:09am PST 

And he has such a beautiful smile! Oh Cookie, we love you so. A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 23, 2016 at 9:53am PST 
He’s an excellent chef… A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 21, 2016 at 1:36pm PST 
…and he’s always down for a fancy meal! A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 20, 2016 at 7:09am PST 
He’s giving, and loves to share, making him our dream dog. A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 19, 2016 at 6:36am PST 
And boy does Cookie ever look ~fly AF~ in glasses! A photo posted by vegan foodie & hungry puppy (@ps.ny) on Dec 18, 2016 at 7:00am PST 
Happy scrolling!
